26Ezk 40:47 He measured the court in the form of a square at 100 cubits long and 100 cubits wide. The altar stood in front of the temple.
26Ezk 40:48 Next, he brought me to the temple porch and measured the side pillars at five cubits on each side. The width of the gate measured three cubits on each side.
