26Ezk 42:3 Opposite the 20 cubits that pertained to the inner court, and opposite the paved area that pertained to the outer court, there were three stories of galleries that faced each other.
26Ezk 42:4 In front of the chambers there was an inner walkway ten cubits wide and 100 cubits wide, the openings to which were on the north.
