26Ezk 46:3 "'The people who live in the land will worship at the doorway of the gate on the sabbaths and new moons in the Lord's presence.
26Ezk 46:4 "'The burnt offering that the Regent Prince will present to the Lord on the Sabbath day will consist of six lambs without defect, a ram without defect,
